item.title: I Need Some Object Help
item.dc:creator: @Darque_Star Darque Star
item.description:
@Darque_Star wrote:

OPEN CLIENT.JAVA ,ok…search

public void NewObjects()
you will see something like this!

[code]public void NewObjects() { // Darque Star ( non laggy !)

makeGlobalObject(3076, 3855, 2213, 0, 10);//bank
makeGlobalObject(3572, 9677, 2478, 0, 10);//altar
makeGlobalObject(2394, 9501, 2213, 0, 10);//bank
makeGlobalObject(2393, 9501, 2213, 0, 10);//bank
makeGlobalObject(3100, 3934, 2213, 0, 10);//bank
makeGlobalObject(3092, 3959, 2213, 0, 10);//bank
makeGlobalObject(3208, 3424, 2213, 0, 10);//bank
makeGlobalObject(3209, 3424, 2213, 0, 10);//bank
makeGlobalObject(3551, 9693, 7273, 0, 10);//barrows portal
makeGlobalObject(2738, 5087, 6409, -1, 10);
makeGlobalObject(3552, 9693, 7324, 0, 10);//big/secret zone[/code]
the makeglobalobject’s are the objects you are making!
the code is like this!

makeGlobalObject(absX, absY, objectID, 0, 10);

see what i mean? i hope this helps you.
